from collections import Counter

num_of_votes = int(input())
votes = [input() for _ in range(num_of_votes)]

c = Counter(votes)

max_count = max(c.values())

print("\n".join(sorted([v for v in c.keys() if c[v] == max_count])))

import sys

import collections

n = int(sys.stdin.readline())
s = [sys.stdin.readline().rstrip() for _ in range(n)]

c = collections.Counter(s)

print("\n".join(sorted(k for k, v in c.items() if v == max(c.values()))))
